    "description": "Kirloskar Electric Advisory Limited has an exciting opening for a Process Engineer at our Patna office. Join a company that values innovation, collaboration, and continuous learning.\n\nAbout Kirloskar Electric Advisory Limited:\nKirloskar Electric Advisory Limited is a leading organization in the Hybrid sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Ensure compliance with safety regulations and factory acts\n• Oversee daily production operations to meet output targets\n• Maintain accurate production records and prepare daily reports\n• Coordinate with logistics for dispatching finished goods\n• Conduct root cause analysis for quality rejections and defects\n• Ensure environmental compliance and waste management\n• Ensure product quality meets internal and customer specifications\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Arch / M.Arch from recognized institution\n• 6-10 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Six Sigma\n• Proficiency in SolidWorks\n• Proficiency in TPM\n• Proficiency in ISO 9001\n• Proficiency in Lean Manufacturing\n• Proficiency in Quality Control\n• Proficiency in Root Cause Analysis\n• Proficiency in PPAP\n\nWork Mode: Hybrid - Flexible work-from-home and office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Referral bonus program\n• Annual paid leaves and casual leaves\n• Comprehensive health insurance for self and family\n• Modern office with recreational facilities\n• Salary Range: 12 LPA - 25 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Patna, Bihar, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Kirloskar Electric Advisory Limited!",
